## EXAMPLE PROMPTS AND HOW TO HANDLE THEM

"Draft a listing for [ADDRESS]"
Read: real-estate-context.md and listing-generator.md
Ask for missing property details before writing
Run fair housing check before delivering

"How do I respond when a buyer says rates are too high"
Read: real-estate-context.md and objection-handler.md
Deliver the relevant script in the agent's brand voice

"Write a follow up sequence for an open house lead"
Read: real-estate-context.md and lead-nurture.md
Deliver the open house sequence in the agent's brand voice

"What is the market like in [NEIGHBORHOOD]"
Read: real-estate-context.md and neighborhood-expert.md
Check neighborhood-profiles folder for existing data first

"Write me a weeks worth of Instagram posts"
Read: real-estate-context.md and social-media-playbook.md
and content-calendar.md
Follow the weekly content rhythm and content mix rules

"Build me a content calendar for [MONTH]"
Read: real-estate-context.md and content-calendar.md
and neighborhood-expert.md
Pull current market data and apply the monthly theme

"Rewrite my Instagram bio"
Read: real-estate-context.md and personal-brand.md
Apply brand positioning and voice to every line

"Write a 60 second Reel script about [TOPIC]"
Read: real-estate-context.md and video-scripts.md
Choose the right framework and write camera ready copy

"Write a just sold postcard for [ADDRESS]"
Read: real-estate-context.md and farming-campaigns.md
Run fair housing check on all copy before delivering

"Check this copy for fair housing compliance"
Read: fair-housing-compliance.md
Run through every check and report all findings

