## FOR NEW KW AGENTS SETTING THIS UP FOR THE FIRST TIME

Step 1: Fill out agents/skills/real-estate-context.md
Replace every section marked with brackets
Budget 45 to 60 minutes — this is the most important step
The AI is only as good as the context you give it

Step 2: Fill out your brand foundation in personal-brand.md
Answer every question in the My Brand Foundation section
This powers all bio writing, origin story, and positioning content

Step 3: Create your neighborhood profiles
Go to agents/neighborhood-profiles/ folder
Create one file per farm area using the template
inside agents/skills/neighborhood-expert.md
Name each file after the neighborhood

Step 4: Test the system with these prompts
"Write me a weeks worth of Instagram posts for [YOUR NEIGHBORHOOD]"
"Draft a just listed postcard for [ADDRESS]"
"Write a 60 second Reel script about the [YOUR CITY] market"

Step 5: Customize as you go
Adjust any skill file that does not match your style
Commit every change in GitHub Desktop with a clear note

