## MAINTENANCE SCHEDULE

agents/skills/real-estate-context.md
Update every month — market conditions and proof points

agents/neighborhood-profiles/
Update every quarter — all data points and recent sales

agents/marketing/content-calendar.md
Update every January — refresh monthly themes with current data

agents/marketing/social-media-playbook.md
Update when platform algorithms or formats change

agents/marketing/farming-campaigns.md
Update when campaign performance data suggests changes

agents/skills/fair-housing-compliance.md
Update when regulations change at federal state or local level